---
import DpostImg from '../images/dpost.png';
import WillowImg from '../images/willowwish.png';
import FosterImg from '../images/tfa.png';
---
<section class="bg-gray-100 py-24 px-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center" id="projects">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6">Projects</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-12">
      A sample of recent work where I helped organizations rethink their digital platforms and deliver lasting impact.
    </p>

    <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-3">
      <!-- Project 1 -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <img src={DpostImg.src} alt="Discount Post Installation" class="w-full h-40 object-cover" />
        <div class="p-5 text-left">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Discount Post: Small Business Site</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">
Developed a streamlined, low-maintenance website and brand identity, enabling a small company to establish its presence while staying focused on its core operations.          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Project 2 -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <img src={FosterImg.src} alt="The Foster Alliance" class="w-full h-40 object-cover" />
        <div class="p-5 text-left">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">The Foster Alliance: Team Augmentation</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">
Stepped in as an integral part of their team, managing website maintenance and updates while executing a much-needed design overhaul to support their nonprofitâ€™s impactful mission.          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Project 3 -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden">
        <img src={WillowImg.src} alt="Willow Wish AZ" class="w-full h-40 object-cover" />
        <div class="p-5 text-left">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Willow Wish AZ: Website Rebuild</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm mb-3">
Designed a clean, low-maintenance website and brand identity, giving a small company the foundation it needed while allowing them to stay focused on their work.          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
